name: Flava T's
description: This is it! The release of the Flava T-Shirt! This is a slim fit design available in black only with chrome lettering. All T-Shirts are hand made and made to order.

name: Flava Original
description: The first and most original hat - hence it name - this hat was the first design we came up with creating style with simplicity, it sports the large flava logo up to with the recognised flava logo up front, sporting a bobble is always cool so we stuck on on there too!
